cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper focuses on semantic reasoning for autonomous driving, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The approach also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques for joint classification, detection, and segmentation. Additionally, natural language processing (cs.CL) may be relevant for the semantic segmentation task.
